{"tid":1037450,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《還願》主動下架 傳內地發行商遭約談","createTime":"2019-02-26T03:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T14:49:13.000Z","uid":43718,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"11ce3ce313608fd3a0bfeff2c2fa79392f5186da","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【惡咒「習維尼」】《還願》主動下架 傳內地發行商遭約談</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n（新增內容）台灣「赤燭遊戲」（下稱赤燭）開發的恐怖新作《還願》（Devotion），因為遊戲中暗藏「習近平小熊維尼」符咒遭中國大陸封殺。有玩家今日凌晨發現，《還願》已從遊戲平台STEAM下架，只剩下原聲帶。赤燭今日6時左右在facebook粉絲專頁發文，稱因《還願》在部份電腦，出現無法開啟與偶有閃退現象，決定先行下架，重新進行軟體品質檢測。<br />\n<br />\n《還願》下架消息一出，網民湧到台灣論壇「批踢踢」抱怨，對照日前爆發的「習維尼」事件，直呼背後有陰謀。赤燭亦澄清，「只是後台處理事情，稍安勿躁」，並呼籲各界利用這段時間，從素材誤植風波中冷靜下來，團隊也會避免類似事情再度發生，「希望《還願》重新上架STEAM時，我們能夠更加專注遊戲本身的內涵。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，仍也有人不滿遊戲遭政治迫害，留言「為甚麼要向中國低頭？」<br />\n<br />\n此外，根據台灣《鏡週刊》報道，中國官方調查《還願》事件，傳北京派人赴上海請發行商「喝茶」。<br />\n<br />\n中國發行商Indievent雖然迅速與赤燭撇清關係，但傳出中共官方已展開深入的調查。在23日《還願》事件在中國全面升溫，Indievent在當日下午3時左右即發出聲明，強調他們是在當天11時左右才得知此事，也隨即進行查核；但因為「最新的版本中」依舊存在「隱喻政治元素」，所以決定終止與赤燭的合作關係。<br />\n<br />\n一位認識Indievent內部人員的台灣遊戲界人士對《鏡週刊》表示，Indievent對赤燭在遊戲中放置這種具有政治意涵的素材是「完全不知情的」；甚至赤燭在21日推出v1.0.5版把素材更新的事情，他們也沒有收到通知。<br />\n<br />\n對照Indievent的官方微博，他們的確在23日當天上午11時52分還有發出一份聲明 （現已無法瀏覽） ，表示「經過測試人員的解包，並沒有發現相關的敏感內容」，並附上符咒素材的圖檔；雖然「呢嘛叭唭」仍然存在 ，但紅色印章篆體字樣是「恭賀新禧」，並非「習近平小熊維尼」。<br />\n<br />\n據另一位時常來往兩岸的遊戲業者透露，業界傳聞中共官方在24日已派出工作組從北京奔赴上海，調查Indievent在這次事件的涉入程度，「恐怕會被請喝茶」；他更評估，Indievent其實也只是新公司，官方微博才剛開，並非多大的發行商，「遇到這樣的事情，很可能就直接倒了。」<br />\n他亦提到，「中國官方原本就已經在加強遊戲監管，未來對外來遊戲（審查）可能會更加嚴格」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》／《鏡週刊》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190226/59303504?fbclid=IwAR19M0pNdGTU2lBJgn6jLJPQWZ6dTWhykW0-hrruChDpoHmjlo9Wm2toZkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59303504%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR19M0pNdGTU2lBJgn6jLJPQWZ6dTWhykW0-hrruChDpoHmjlo9Wm2toZkE&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnffQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=d5232b3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190226%2F59303504%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR19M0pNdGTU2lBJgn6jLJPQWZ6dTWhykW0-hrruChDpoHmjlo9Wm2toZkE&h=d0280b14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190226/59303504?fbclid=IwAR19M0pNdGTU2lBJgn6jLJPQWZ6dTWhykW0-hrruChDpoHmjlo9Wm2toZkE</a>"},{"pid":"fb4ae7d101cf5c19d5dfeabed01e68ca98f28cdf","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb0079523ff9d9de89f715945b6708e4c32eb02","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5c771f89b442c31fe12fb4dc03e11e5c64e1cb","tid":1037450,"uid":41355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"中共百年歷史以來都是這副德性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e10d4aaab33f1c56a1cfd0ff2c1c99206b99183","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755a63f4d14636b3cc926dd01e6fb793e09105e3","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5665ef262a3e62ce269efbd9db8c5d3188b84945","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e1f979c04d2cb2535153ecab41343706b3f6e8","tid":1037450,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:21:57.000Z","msg":"文革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245ad769c1060793e6668695521495c8a306f07c","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f7f63e7be20e7676153c8b2881a490f83a17dc","tid":1037450,"uid":90259,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"呢件事只係冰山一角，喺steam成千上萬隻遊戲，根本冇可能全部檢查文本同內容，即使發行商都無可能阻止製作方的惡意滲透反革命思想<br />\n<br />\n身處中國土地，大家應該一人一信廣電總局，要求全面禁止steam再喺大陸散播低俗國外遊戲荼毒國民，保護良善風俗，只允許中國境內公司製作的遊戲在國內流通，方便指導和處理"},{"pid":"230277b67d9ecd84b513bb59c0ec38ce9d2309f1","tid":1037450,"uid":52598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"刁總成日話要禁遊戲，幾時禁埋steam呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />還中國人民一個良好的社會環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3fe946a06a2677f2c1ad45e5d9c4cef27eeccf","tid":1037450,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fb5827e087b1a41cd804dceaa5d72d05610ac45","tid":1037450,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f3fe946a06a2677f2c1ad45e5d9c4cef27eeccf","tid":1037450,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ab5c771f89b442c31fe12fb4dc03e11e5c64e1cb","tid":1037450,"uid":41355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"中共百年歷史以來都是這副德性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:35:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"WIKI:<br />\n<br />\n成立 <br />\n1921年7月23日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家要玩睇怕要下載盜版了?"},{"pid":"0de2c9d58ee7d813d456800dfff83126f03ef808","tid":1037450,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"他亦提到，「中國官方原本就已經在加強遊戲監管，未來對外來遊戲（審查）可能會更加嚴格」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a846f193120a7beb43f52525ba9975a64e59ed","tid":1037450,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"930af2456ab0fd3fe45c2d4db7124a31ab1c8527","tid":1037450,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"遊戲台都有5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"1c59a69209d316992a629d52709d426e19e72bcc","tid":1037450,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:50:29.000Z","msg":"支持支那bam steam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8456475e743f1de5a429461f18906c78e3a85b","tid":1037450,"uid":67454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"01f7f63e7be20e7676153c8b2881a490f83a17dc","tid":1037450,"uid":90259,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"呢件事只係冰山一角，喺steam成千上萬隻遊戲，根本冇可能全部檢查文本同內容，即使發行商都無可能阻止製作方的惡意滲透反革命思想<br />\n<br />\n身處中國土地，大家應該一人一信廣電總局，要求全面禁止steam再喺大陸散播低俗國外遊戲荼毒國民，保護良善風俗，只允許中國境內公司製作的遊戲在國內流通，方便指導和處理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n所有西洋遊戲應該全部封鎖，以後此等遊戲只能禍害歐美夷狄<br />\n<br />\n而且中國遊戲玩家技術強大，以fps遊戲為首更是猶如神仙，列國根本無資格與天朝上國對抗，故應徹底隔絕雙方，以免夷狄偷學我國神技"},{"pid":"d5ae56741407fe6a9ebae8cbaebeb000f485d145","tid":1037450,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556bdd2ae2aecd937b18